Package: krebs
Title: Krebs - Multi-tenant Oncology Cancer Registry
Version: 0.2.0
Authors@R: person("Fabian A.", "Gutierrez Valle", email = "0201270@up.edu.mx", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Shiny application for multi-institution oncology cancer registries.
    Implements WHO-aligned data capture (TNM, ICD-O-3, CPT), longitudinal
    follow-up with recurrence tracking, role-based access control, and
    interactive dashboards. Backed by PostgreSQL with row-level security
    for multi-tenant isolation.
